<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA1">
<l>muyaṟṟi cumanteḻuntu muntuṟṟa neñcē</l>
<l>yiyaṟṟuvā yemmoṭunī kūṭi nayappuṭaiya</l>
<l>nāvīṉ toṭaikkiḷavi yuḷpotivō naṟpūvaip</l>
<l>pūvīṉṟa vaṇṇaṉ pukaḻ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O heart that, bearing the effort, rises [and] is before [him],</l>
<l>you joining us, with peforming mouths, we shall store up</l>
<l>in woven words brought forth by tongues that have longing</l>
<l>the praise of him with flower colour who brought forth the good flower.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
